                            <comment id="12714916" author="apurtell" created="Sun, 31 May 2009 18:58:22 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Enabling this is one reason why we put region information into HServerLoad&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12717851" author="stack" created="Tue, 9 Jun 2009 22:52:32 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Best done as part of master rewrite.  Moving it out.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12904928" author="streamy" created="Wed, 1 Sep 2010 05:41:43 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Now that master rewrite is done, I&apos;m unclear of the scope of this jira.  Is this fixed?  HMaster gets confirmation of open via zk, should only be closed if the master asks him to be closed or if RS dies, which is handled in server expire.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12905107" author="stack" created="Wed, 1 Sep 2010 17:40:46 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Closing as won&apos;t fix.  Lets open a more specific issue, one that addresses a particular problem with new method of region assignment, rather than let this general description hang out as an open issue.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="15017755" author="lars_francke" created="Fri, 20 Nov 2015 13:01:15 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This issue was closed as part of a bulk closing operation on 2015-11-20. All issues that have been resolved and where all fixVersions have been released have been closed (following discussions on the mailing list).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
